   1 # -*- coding=utf-8 -*-
   2 
   3 from __future__ import absolute_import, print_function, unicode_literals
   4 
   5 from resolvelib import NoVersionsAvailable, ResolutionImpossible
   6 
   7 from passa.internals.reporters import print_requirement
   8 
   9 
  10 def lock(locker):
  11     success = False
  12     try:
  13         locker.lock()
  14     except NoVersionsAvailable as e:
  15         print("\nCANNOT RESOLVE. NO CANDIDATES FOUND FOR:")
  16         print("{:>40}".format(e.requirement.as_line(include_hashes=False)))
  17         if e.parent:
  18             line = e.parent.as_line(include_hashes=False)
  19             print("{:>41}".format("(from {})".format(line)))
  20         else:
  21             print("{:>41}".format("(user)"))
  22     except ResolutionImpossible as e:
  23         print("\nCANNOT RESOLVE.\nOFFENDING REQUIREMENTS:")
  24         for r in e.requirements:
  25             print_requirement(r)
  26     else:
  27         success = True
  28     return success
